12
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,480
Lyu Xing

13
00:01:50,800 --> 00:01:51,600
Lyu Xing

14
00:01:53,360 --> 00:01:54,120
Lyu Xing

15
00:01:56,160 --> 00:01:57,400
Get out of the way

16
00:01:57,600 --> 00:01:58,560
Move

17
00:02:01,320 --> 00:02:03,400
You're calling this bracelet Lyu Xing?

18
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:05,280
You're just messing with me

19
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:05,840
Lin You

20
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:07,880
You wanna die? It really is Lyu Xing

21
00:02:07,880 --> 00:02:08,919
Tell me, is it really Lyu Xing?

22
00:02:08,919 --> 00:02:10,320
How dare you draw me so ugly

23
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:12,080
I'm gonna...

24
00:02:14,720 --> 00:02:15,920
Uncle Wang's calling me over

25
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:18,760
I...

26
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:20,440
Coming

27
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:21,840
Hold on

28
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:23,040
I'm gonna need this stuff

29
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,840
Follow my lead in a bit

30
00:02:30,880 --> 00:02:31,680
Lin You

31
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:53,360
Master.

32
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:55,360
