65
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:51,360
All done.

66
00:04:52,320 --> 00:04:52,880
Let's go.

67
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:02,240
Bro,

68
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:04,480
honestly, I knew

69
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:06,200
