70
00:05:08,400 --> 00:05:09,840
Then why did you keep up the act?

71
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,640
And got Daji to sell houses for you?

72
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:16,200
I didn't even know her,

73
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:19,080
but I just feel it's unfair.

74
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:22,360
Why do the killers get to live perfectly fine

75
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:25,200
while the dead never even get an apology?

76
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:26,720
What did they do?

77
00:05:27,760 --> 00:05:29,120
Didn't Lyu Xing kill herself?

78
00:05:36,840 --> 00:05:38,640
I've only been at this company a month.

79
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:41,240
My current workstation

80
00:05:42,960 --> 00:05:44,520
used to belong to Lyu Xing.

81
00:05:49,040 --> 00:05:50,200
What's going on with this budget?

82
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:52,200
Because of you,

83
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:54,560
this morning, Mr. Qin

84
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:56,600
