85
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:58,520
Wang Yu,

86
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:01,200
you handled the first part.

87
00:06:01,280 --> 00:06:03,360
Why is the budget off by so much?

88
00:06:07,480 --> 00:06:08,320
And you,

89
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,960
Yell at them, but leave me out of it.

90
00:06:13,520 --> 00:06:14,800
I just do the final check.

91
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,280
Sorry, Mr. Zhang.

92
00:06:20,320 --> 00:06:21,280
It's my fault.

93
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:23,320
When Xiaoyu sent me the first draft,

94
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:24,880
I didn't check it carefully.

95
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:26,120
The amount was miscalculated.

96
00:06:26,840 --> 00:06:28,240
That's how Sister Na got dragged in.

97
00:06:29,640 --> 00:06:30,800
Oh, so you do know!

98
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:35,160
Now get the hell out!

99
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:39,400
Stop your sniveling!

100
00:06:40,520 --> 00:06:41,120
Let me tell you,

101
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:42,680
get it right, then hand it to me.

102
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:43,440
Got it?

103
00:06:44,520 --> 00:06:45,280
Yes, Mr. Zhang.

104
00:06:45,280 --> 00:06:46,440
I'll redo it right away.

105
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:47,080
Move it!

106
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:55,840
Why'd you yell at me?

107
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:56,640
I...

108
00:06:58,560 --> 00:06:59,760
just wanted to scare them a bit.

109
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:05,080
Mr. Qin wants to keep her as a mistress.

110
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:13,240
Then what? Then what?

111
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:14,360
Sis,

112
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:16,280
I really don't know more.

113
00:07:17,280 --> 00:07:18,080
What if...

114
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:23,240
What if Xingxing likes Mr. Qin too?

115
00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:25,840
Little sis,

116
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:28,840
you definitely know the inside story.

117
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:31,400
Let me tell you,

118
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:34,400
promotion slots at our company are limited.

119
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:36,640
As long as I

120
00:07:37,160 --> 00:07:39,040
give Old Zhang a little signal,

121
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:41,040
you get what I mean?

122
00:07:42,760 --> 00:07:44,040
What exactly do you know?

123
00:07:54,840 --> 00:07:55,640
Seriously.

124
00:07:56,640 --> 00:07:57,440
Oh my God.

125
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:58,680
This is so juicy.

126
00:07:58,880 --> 00:07:59,680
Xiaoyu.

127
00:08:00,520 --> 00:08:01,320
You there?

128
00:08:09,200 --> 00:08:10,000
What are you doing?

129
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:13,520
I didn't want to embarrass you in public.

130
00:08:14,840 --> 00:08:15,680
Tell me.

131
00:08:16,400 --> 00:08:17,760
Are we still good friends or not?

132
00:08:19,960 --> 00:08:20,760
Yeah, we are.

133
00:08:21,320 --> 00:08:22,320
As your friend,

134
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:24,680
I took the blame for you.

135
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:28,320
But if you really see me as a friend,

136
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,240
why would you

137
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,280
go blabbing about me and Mr. Qin

138
00:08:31,280 --> 00:08:32,159
to Sister Na?

139
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:34,440
That's ridiculous.

140
00:08:34,799 --> 00:08:35,440
I didn't.

141
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:56,240
All you ever do is cry, huh?

142
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:58,800
Who are you crying for?

143
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:02,480
Hurry up and finish this stuff.

144
00:09:03,040 --> 00:09:04,760
I need it for my report tomorrow morning.

145
00:09:04,760 --> 00:09:06,280
I've already finished my work.

146
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:10,920
This isn't my job.

147
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:12,680
I have to hurry back home.

148
00:09:12,680 --> 00:09:14,080
It's my son's birthday.

149
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:16,480
Can you just hurry up?

150
00:09:18,680 --> 00:09:19,560
Either do it or get out.

151
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:21,000
Unbelievable.

152
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:22,720
Go find your Mr. Qin.

153
00:09:22,920 --> 00:09:24,080
Go tattle on me, then.

154
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:26,800
Give me a break.

155
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:34,960
Hello, Mom.

156
00:09:35,800 --> 00:09:36,680
What are you up to?

157
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:40,480
I'm having dinner.

158
00:09:41,920 --> 00:09:43,120
Today is your birthday.

159
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:44,160
Do you remember?

160
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:46,520
Remember to eat noodles.

161
00:09:48,760 --> 00:09:49,840
I remember, Mom.

162
00:09:50,920 --> 00:09:51,560
Okay.

163
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:53,520
Did you have cake then?

164
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:56,480
Yes, I did.

165
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:58,920
Is Xiaoyu there with you?

166
00:10:04,760 --> 00:10:05,360
Yes.

167
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:07,040
Xiaoyu's keeping me company.

168
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:08,160
Good, good, good.

169
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:09,760
Then Mom can relax.

170
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:11,440
Alright, then.

171
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:12,320
You two have fun.

172
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:13,120
I'm hanging up.

173
00:10:14,040 --> 00:10:15,000
Remember, don't stay up too late.

174
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:16,000
Cut back on takeout.

175
00:10:16,040 --> 00:10:17,200
Take good care of yourself.

176
00:10:17,400 --> 00:10:18,040
Bye-bye.

177
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:57,240
We have to do something for Lyu Xing.

178
00:10:58,800 --> 00:10:59,600
At the very least,

179
00:11:01,880 --> 00:11:03,080
we have to clear her name.

180
00:11:37,280 --> 00:11:37,920
Brother Zhang

181
00:11:40,040 --> 00:11:41,400
Do you really enjoy

182
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:43,040
making others take the fall?

183
00:11:43,560 --> 00:11:45,400
Do you know how awful it feels

184
00:11:45,400 --> 00:11:46,920
to be wrongly accused?

185
00:11:47,600 --> 00:11:48,480
I'm sorry, Xiao Lyu.

186
00:11:48,920 --> 00:11:49,960
I... I'm sorry.

187
00:11:50,520 --> 00:11:51,160
I was wrong.

188
00:11:52,320 --> 00:11:53,120
I was wrong.

189
00:11:53,360 --> 00:11:54,240
I was wrong.

190
00:11:54,240 --> 00:11:55,280
I was truly wrong.

191
00:11:55,400 --> 00:11:56,520
I'm begging your forgiveness.

192
00:11:56,560 --> 00:11:57,480
I'll kowtow to you.

193
00:11:57,480 --> 00:11:58,360
I'll kowtow to you.

194
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:00,000
I was wrong.

195
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:01,480
Xiao Lyu, I was wrong.

196
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:07,160
Sister Na.

197
00:12:11,680 --> 00:12:12,320
Sister Na.

198
00:12:12,320 --> 00:12:13,200
Stay back!

199
00:12:14,400 --> 00:12:16,560
Why do you get to happily

200
00:12:16,560 --> 00:12:18,240
celebrate your son's birthday,

201
00:12:19,520 --> 00:12:21,280
while I work overtime for you?

202
00:12:22,320 --> 00:12:24,480
Do you really love gossip that much?

203
00:12:25,160 --> 00:12:26,240
Don't come any closer!

204
00:12:26,440 --> 00:12:27,240
Xingxing.

205
00:12:27,680 --> 00:12:28,480
It's my fault.

206
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:30,440
I was wrong.

207
00:12:31,160 --> 00:12:33,560
I'll burn extra spirit money for you, okay?

208
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:35,920
Every grievance has its source.

209
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:37,240
Go find her.

210
00:12:37,680 --> 00:12:39,080
Go find her!

211
00:12:45,160 --> 00:12:46,040
Xiaoyu.

212
00:12:49,920 --> 00:12:51,400
You were my best friend.

213
00:12:53,520 --> 00:12:55,520
We had so many wonderful memories.

214
00:12:58,120 --> 00:12:59,560
I kept thinking,

215
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:02,480
if you'd thought of me even once,

216
00:13:03,040 --> 00:13:05,160
I'd appear in your dreams.

217
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:07,840
But you never did, not once.

218
00:13:09,920 --> 00:13:10,560
Xingxing.

219
00:13:10,560 --> 00:13:11,360
Just kill me.

220
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:12,560
Take me with you.

221
00:13:14,240 --> 00:13:15,560
Take me with you.

222
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:18,200
Stop this.

223
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:21,800
Wang Yu.

224
00:13:22,120 --> 00:13:23,000
Let me tell you,

225
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:24,400
Lyu Xing's death

226
00:13:25,680 --> 00:13:26,880
wasn't just because of you.

227
00:13:32,160 --> 00:13:33,320
Every single one of you

228
00:13:34,760 --> 00:13:35,760
shares the blame.

229
00:13:37,640 --> 00:13:39,480
She suffered so much injustice,

230
00:13:40,520 --> 00:13:42,240
yet still thought of all of you.

231
00:13:43,720 --> 00:13:44,520
And what about you?

232
00:13:46,160 --> 00:13:47,400
Did you ever think of her?

233
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:50,160
Even once?

234
00:13:57,640 --> 00:13:58,840
You're only scared now,

235
00:14:00,640 --> 00:14:01,960
that's why you're apologizing.

236
00:14:04,440 --> 00:14:05,720
If even one of you back then

237
00:14:05,720 --> 00:14:07,240
had thought of her even once,

238
00:14:09,040 --> 00:14:10,800
would she have ended up like this?

239
00:14:12,160 --> 00:14:12,960
Would she?

240
00:14:21,800 --> 00:14:22,400
Wang Yu.

241
00:14:26,080 --> 00:14:27,520
You were the friend she cared about most.

242
00:14:32,080 --> 00:14:33,400
Even when you betrayed her,

243
00:14:35,480 --> 00:14:36,640
she never once thought

244
00:14:36,640 --> 00:14:38,400
about giving up your friendship.

245
00:14:39,880 --> 00:14:40,840
But what about you?

246
00:14:42,600 --> 00:14:44,720
Look at what you've done.

247
00:14:45,920 --> 00:14:48,080
Can you live with yourself after this?

248
00:14:49,840 --> 00:14:51,400
All she ever wanted

249
00:14:51,400 --> 00:14:52,680
was a word of comfort,

250
00:14:52,680 --> 00:14:53,360
a hug.

251
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:54,560
Was that so hard?

252
00:14:55,760 --> 00:14:57,000
You couldn't even do that?

253
00:15:01,240 --> 00:15:01,720
Fine.

254
00:15:01,920 --> 00:15:03,040
They couldn't do it.

255
00:15:04,360 --> 00:15:05,360
I understand.

256
00:15:10,320 --> 00:15:11,880
But why you?

257
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:16,800
Xingxing.

258
00:15:17,560 --> 00:15:18,760
I was wrong.

259
00:15:19,760 --> 00:15:22,520
The messages you sent me before you left,

260
00:15:22,520 --> 00:15:23,240
the calls you made,

261
00:15:23,240 --> 00:15:24,520
I saw them all.

262
00:15:25,480 --> 00:15:26,840
I just didn't have the courage.

263
00:15:27,480 --> 00:15:29,040
I couldn't face you.

264
00:15:31,200 --> 00:15:33,760
I was jealous you were better than me at everything.

265
00:15:34,160 --> 00:15:36,160
That's why I talked nonsense.

266
00:15:37,160 --> 00:15:37,960
Xingxing.

267
00:15:38,200 --> 00:15:39,000
Xingxing.

268
00:15:39,160 --> 00:15:40,640
Xingxing, I was wrong.

269
00:15:40,760 --> 00:15:42,480
Please forgive me.

270
00:15:50,520 --> 00:15:51,600
It's not too late.

271
00:15:53,920 --> 00:15:55,280
We're performing this ritual

272
00:15:56,080 --> 00:15:57,680
not just for Lyu Xing,

273
00:16:01,120 --> 00:16:03,320
but so the living can find peace.

274
00:16:04,400 --> 00:16:05,760
I once heard an old master

275
00:16:05,760 --> 00:16:06,720
say something.

276
00:16:08,160 --> 00:16:09,360
He said people who take their own lives

277
00:16:11,320 --> 00:16:13,320
can't see what's truly wrong.

278
00:16:14,520 --> 00:16:16,600
So they're trapped in their own suffering,

279
00:16:16,800 --> 00:16:19,360
reliving that pain over and over.

280
00:16:21,640 --> 00:16:22,960
Only when they realize

281
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:26,120
that suicide solves nothing

282
00:16:29,360 --> 00:16:30,440
can they finally find release.

283
00:16:39,880 --> 00:16:42,320
Your apologies matter, of course.

284
00:16:43,440 --> 00:16:44,680
But what matters more

285
00:16:46,800 --> 00:16:49,240
is facing up to your own cruelty.

286
00:16:56,800 --> 00:16:58,520
Master... Master Lin.

287
00:17:09,839 --> 00:17:11,160
I'm running out of time.

288
00:17:12,760 --> 00:17:13,680
You all...

289
00:17:14,520 --> 00:17:16,160
watch yourselves.

290
00:17:23,760 --> 00:17:24,560
Mr. Qin.

291
00:17:25,079 --> 00:17:27,800
I asked you to find an agent to rent the place out,

292
00:17:28,440 --> 00:17:30,160
